Map Favorite Profile Photos Map Reviews Profile Cucu’s Nest Bar has a history back to early 2000s when it was a hot spot and a dive bar for locals. Little by little it was turning to a  favorite place among tourists who were coming back to the bar their every visit to Miami. Caring the best warm  memories from making friends during happy hour drink, parties till 5 a.m. with karaoke, pool and hot outgoing bartenders, Cucu’s Nest Bar now reopened on South Beach!
